my fix is ```def module totemTest
def desc "Custom Scripted Module"

on tick on key_press e {
    switch #totem
}
if input_active inventory {
    gui_quickmove #totem 9
    if off_holding #air,#shield {
        gui_swap #totem
    }
}
 and if there are 2 totems in the players hot bar it switches to the one closest to 1 so iif the player gets popped the player will only have a totem in their offhand